  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to wpebackend-fdo</title>

    <para>
      The <application>wpebackend-fdo</application> package contains the
      Freedesktop.org backend for WPE WebKit and the WPE renderer.
    </para>

    &lfs110a_checked;

